{"word":"G4438 - πυκτέω - pyktéō - pook-teh'-o - Fight","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">πυκτέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">pyktéō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">pook-teh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Fight</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - சிலம்பம் பண்ணு"},{"paragraph":"to be a boxer, to box fight"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From a derivative of the same as <a href=\"#/G4435 - πυγμή - pygmḗ - poog-may'/4435\">G4435</a>; to <i>box</i> (with the fist), that is, <i>contend</i> (as a boxer) at the games (figuratively): - fight.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G4435/4435\">G4435</a>, <a href=\"#/G4438/4438\">G4438</a>"}]}